title UC5 - Configure Rules

start

:1. Admin accesses Configure Rules page;
:2. System fetches all available rules;
:3. System displays current rule settings;

:4. Admin selects rules to enable/disable;
:5. Admin sets severity levels;
:6. Admin configures rule thresholds;
:7. Admin sets quality gates;

:8. System validates rule configuration;

if (9. Configuration valid?) then (Yes)
  :10. Admin reviews rule summary;
else (No)
  :11. Display validation errors;
endif

if (12. Admin approves?) then (Yes)
  :13. Save rule configuration;
  :14. Update active rule set;
  :15. Display success message;
else (No)
  :16. Admin modifies rules;
